Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.65,0:18:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.86,0:18:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Em không muốn anh rời khỏi em...
